---
title: Pork Bulgogi Bowls with Carrots, Pickled Cucumber & Sriracha Crema
description: If you can’t seem to get enough of Korean-inspired flavors, bulgogi is sure to leave you satisfied. This dish centers around pork cooked in a sesame and soy sauce marinade with a little bit of peppery sweetness. But the meat is just one out of many highlights: There’s also crisp quick-pickled cucumbers, tender carrots, and spicy crema, all over fluffy rice—each bowl is jam-packed and has a little bit of something for everyone.
